Package com.samsung.android.sdk.visualview

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SVSlideManager.ImplicitAnimationListener
    This listener interface provides callback methods for implicit animation events your application can implement this interface to get the desired result on start/repeat/End of implicit animation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SV
    This class provides access to the Visual View Package.
    SVColor
    This class holds the data for an RGBA color object in the Visual View package.
    SVGLSurface
    This class provides the drawing surface functionality for the Visual View package.
    SVImage
    This class holds the data for an image object in the Visual View package.
    SVPoint
    This class holds the data for a point object in the Visual View package.
    SVRect
    This class holds the data for a rectangle object in the Visual View package.
    SVSlide
    This class defines a Visual View package slide object.
    SVSlideManager
    This class controls the implicit animation.
    SVVector3
    This class holds data for 3 dimensional vector objects in the Visual View package.
    SVVector4
    This class holds data for 4 dimensional vector objects in the Visual View package.
